<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">为全方位筑牢辅导员队伍根基，提升大家的综合素质与团队协作能力，让每一位辅导员在工作中找到归属感，经济管理学院全体辅导员参与素质拓展活动。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">（一）一圈到底（热身项目）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449528018.jpg" alt="1746449528018.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449528018.jpg" style="width: 674.42px;height: 505.81px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">（二）手脚并用（团队接力）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449561089.jpg" alt="1746449561089.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449561089.jpg" style="width: 674.42px;height: 505.81px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">（三）滚雪球</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449596049.jpg" alt="1746449596049.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449596049.jpg" style="width: 678.42px;height: 452.76px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">（四）压力气球爆破仪式</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449628895.jpg" alt="1746449628895.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449628895.jpg" style="width: 681.42px;height: 453.65px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">（五）同心杆</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449657661.jpg" alt="1746449657661.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449657661.jpg" style="width: 681.42px;height: 511.06px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">（六）团队猜灯谜游戏</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449685384.jpg" alt="1746449685384.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449685384.jpg" style="width: 683.42px;height: 512.56px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">活动结语</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449720143.jpg" alt="1746449720143.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746449720143.jpg" style="width: 683.42px;height: 512.56px;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">本次辅导员心理素质拓展活动在欢声笑语中圆满落幕。从趣味盎然的小游戏，到挑战重重的团队项目，大家都全身心投入，在信任与协作中拉近了彼此距离。不仅释放了工作压力，更增强了团队的凝聚力和归属感。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">未来，希望大家带着这份温暖与力量，以更加积极乐观的态度和更紧密的团队协作，投入到学生工作中，共同助力同学们成长，为学院发展添砖加瓦！</span></p>